original_title: 「青春終わらないで」 部活と恋愛に学生生活を捧げた18歳のちょっぴりクールなバスケ美少女AVデビュー 葵爽
overview: An 18-year-old basketball girl who has just graduated and debuted from Aipoke. Aoi Sou-chan says she wanted to be more in love when she was young and focused on club activities. Her personality looks a little cool, but she is a sweet and kind girl with a smile. She has been playing basketball for 10 years and she was mainly a forward. It was a super sensitive constitution that squirted so much that the sheets were soaked by the technique of a professional actor who experienced it for the first time in the shooting.
title: “I Don’t Want My Adolescence to End.” AV Debut of a Slightly Cool 18 Year Old Basketball Beauty Who Dedicated Her Student Life to Club Activities and Love. Sayaka Aoi.
